Package: bikerentaldata
Title: Historical U.S. Bike-Share Trip Data Tools
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R:
    c(
      person(
        given = "Christopher",
        family = "Odoom",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "odoomchristopher22@gmail.com"
      )
    )
Description: Discovers, downloads, and standardizes official historical trip
    archives from Capital Bikeshare, Citi Bike, Divvy, and Bay Wheels. It
    builds combined multi-city datasets, enriches trips with calendar and
    city-specific weather variables, summarizes station locations, prepares
    daily Capital Bikeshare analysis data, and validates processed data. The
    package contains processing code but does not redistribute the full
    third-party datasets.
